cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.GR 

This paper deals with color constancy in digital cameras, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method is based on unsupervised learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the creation of a new benchmark dataset, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR).
